          </external-xref>)</cato:entity> is amended by striking <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:1862/ss:b/p:5">paragraph
			 (5)</cato:entity-ref>.</text>
			</subsection>
      <subsection id="HD34833FD5DD54FC68F94A3F8F12A3A90">
        <enum>(b)</enum>
        <header>Effective date</header>
        <text>The amendment made by <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Medicare Employer Relief Act of 2014/s:2/ss:a" proposed="true">subsection (a)</cato:entity-ref> shall take effect on the date of the enactment of this Act and
			 shall apply to information required to be provided on or after January 1,
			 2015.</text>
